(310,1,"2018-06-22 23:37:26","2018-06-22 23:37:26","\n	<h1>LACE CURTAINS FOR SET DECORATION</h1>\n<p>Cooper Lace has become the preferred and leading supplier of lace curtains to the Entertainment Industry. We stock extra-long lace curtain panels in lengths of up to 144\" and offer the fastest turnaround times on your orders, typically in 48 hours. Set decorators and buyers know that Cooper Lace will provide them with the most personal, fastest service possible, and we\'ll work through the night and on weekends (just like you do) as we monitor your shipments round-the-clock to keep you apprised of your order\'s status.</p>\n","Set Decorations","","inherit","closed","closed","","30-revision-v1","","","2018-06-22 23:37:26","2018-06-22 23:37:26","",30,"http://cottagelace.local/30-revision-v1/",0,"revision","",0),
(311,1,"2018-06-22 23:39:52","2018-06-22 23:39:52","\n	<h1>SAMPLES</h1>\n<h3>Not Sure Which Pattern Is Best For You?</h3>\n<h3><i>Try Our Free Lace-On-Loan Program!</i></h3>\n<p>Cooper Lace will gladly loan you factory seconds of our lace curtains if you would like to borrow one or more patterns for a couple of weeks; all we ask is a telephone call or email with your name, address, contact information and your desired patterns. We\'ll then rush them out to you, and all you need do is pay for the return postage. The response from our clients to this program has been wildly enthusiastic!</p>\n","Sample Curtains","","inherit","closed","closed","","95-revision-v1","","","2018-06-22 23:39:52","2018-06-22 23:39:52","",95,"http://cottagelace.local/95-revision-v1/",0,"revision","",0),
(312,1,"2018-06-22 23:46:33","2018-06-22 23:46:33","\n	<h1>MEASURING AND CARE OF COOPER LACE CURTAINS</h1>\n<h2>Care and Cleaning of Cooper Lace Curtains</h2>\n<p><b>QUICK TIP:</b> When you first hang your new lace curtains, you\'ll notice that they might be creased from the packaging, but don\'t bother ironing them! Here\'s an easy trick: after they\'re hung, just \'spritz\' them with water from a spray bottle, and they\'ll \'relax\' and settle out nicely!</p>\n<p><b>We strongly suggest dry-cleaning of Exclusive Madras lace curtains!</b> For our Historic and Traditional lines, which are Nottingham lace, we have found that washing them in cold water with a mild detergent, either by hand or on the delicate cycle, works quite well. We use a high-efficiency, front-loading washer, and this leaves the curtains barely damp upon completion of the cycle.</p>\n","Measuring/Care","","inherit","closed","closed","","98-revision-v1","","","2018-06-22 23:46:33","2018-06-22 23:46:33","",98,"http://cottagelace.local/98-revision-v1/",0,"revision","",0),
(313,1,"2018-06-22 23:48:10","2018-06-22 23:48:10","\n	<h1>LACE CURTAINS FOR MUSEUMS</h1>\n<h2>Museum Professionals:</h2>\n<p>Cooper Lace has provided many museums and historic houses with accurate reproduction lace curtain panels throughout the United States, Canada, Europe and Australia. Curators frequently turn to us for both in-stock items and replicating their existing documented patterns. We offer the most reasonable prices, free shipping and the shortest lead times of any lace curtain company.</p>\n","Museum Reproductions","","inherit","closed","closed","","117-revision-v1","","","2018-06-22 23:48:10","2018-06-22 23:48:10","",117,"http://cottagelace.local/117-revision-v1/",0,"revision","",0),
