(408,1,"2018-08-19 22:26:49","2018-08-19 22:26:49","The introduction of Galaxy lace curtains marks the first time a lace curtain panel has been cre-ated to accompany the revival of the Mid-Century Modern style of the 1950s and 1960s. Cooper lace saw a clear need for a lace curtain that provides a clean, simple pattern for those dwelling only slightly in the past. Cooper Lace’s latest curtain pattern, Galaxy, is unique and contempo-rary, and offers a perfect combination of privacy and light. Designed by Steve Bauer of Bradbury &amp; Bradbury Art Wallpapers, Galaxy lace curtains compliment Bradbury’s many exquisite Mid-Century Modern Wallpapers.\r\n\r\n100% Scottish Cotton, finished in Ivory. Custom shortening available.\r\nAvailable in Ivory; custom lengths available.\r\nWoven with a rod pocket and header at the top.","Galaxy","","publish","open","closed","","galaxy","","","2018-08-19 22:27:07","2018-08-19 22:27:07","",0,"http://cottagelace.local/?post_type=product&#038;p=408",0,"product","",0),
