(552,1,"2018-08-24 01:26:34","2018-08-24 01:26:34","<p align=\"LEFT\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica Neue, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"en-US\">Grecian is an Exclusive Cooper Lace pattern woven in </span><span lang=\"it-IT\">100% Scottish Cotton</span><span lang=\"en-US\"> Madras</span>, <span lang=\"en-US\">and finished in Ivory. Madras is a painstakingly-manufactured textured weave applied over a fine scrim mesh and is renown for its detail and depth. This pattern is woven in three widths and available in stock and custom lengths. Custom shortening is available for $10/panel; please order the stock size longer than your desired custom length and indicate it on the order form.  </span></span></span></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica Neue, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"en-US\">All panels are delivered with a 1-1/2” rod pocket and 1” decorative header above it (unless otherwise requested). Bottom rod pockets will be added upon request. International shipping is available.</span></span></span></span></p>","Grecian","<span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"en-US\">Grecian Lace Curtains are perfect for those seeking an exceptional Neo-Classical lace curtain panel. When we began researching an appropriate pattern, we thought, who better to ask than Steve Bauer of </span></span></span><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><span lang=\"zxx\"><u><a href=\"https://bradbury.com/\"><span lang=\"en-US\">Bradbury &amp; Bradbury wallpapers</span></a></u></span></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"en-US\">, the man and the company who created the famous Neo-Grec and Neo-Classical wallpaper roomsets, along with many Colonial Revival wallpapers.</span></span></span>\r\n<p align=\"LEFT\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"en-US\">Featuring popular Classical motifs, our 100% cotton Grecian curtain panel is an elegant enhancement to any room, and is suitable for Georgian, Federal, Greek Revival and Mid-Victorian Houses, as its delicate Classical design is the most harmonious for these styles of interiors. This lace sheer is also intended to ornament Colonial Revival interiors from 1890-1910.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"LEFT\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica Neue, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"en-US\">Extra-Long panels available </span></span></span></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica Neue, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"en-US\">on request. Please <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><u><b><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https://www.cottagelace.local/contact/\">contact us</a></b></u><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"http://cottagelace.local/sample-curtains/\"> </a></span>or <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"http://cottagelace.local/sample-curtains/\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">request a sample panel on loan</span></a></strong></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"LEFT\"></p>","publish","open","closed","","grecian","","","2018-08-28 00:49:58","2018-08-28 00:49:58","",0,"http://cottagelace.local/?post_type=product&#038;p=552",0,"product","",0),
